# Motorsport Modules

Core motorsport domain modules in the `package/src/Motorsport` directory.

## Core Modules

- `Motorsport/Leaderboard.elm` - Race leaderboard functionality
- `Motorsport/RaceControl.elm` - Race control functionality
- `Motorsport/Analysis.elm` - Race data analysis tools
- `Motorsport/Lap.elm` - Lap timing data models
- `Motorsport/LapStatus.elm` - Status information for laps

## Timing and Duration

- `Motorsport/Clock.elm` - Clock and timing utilities
- `Motorsport/Duration.elm` - Duration and time interval models
- `Motorsport/Gap.elm` - Gap between cars/drivers

## Race Participants

- `Motorsport/Car.elm` - Car data models
- `Motorsport/Driver.elm` - Driver information
- `Motorsport/Class.elm` - Car classification

## Charts and Visualization

- `Motorsport/Chart` - Chart components
  - `Motorsport/Chart/LapTime.elm` - Lap time visualization
  - `Motorsport/Chart/Position.elm` - Position changes visualization
- `DataView.elm` - Core visualization components
- `TypedSvg` - SVG utilities

## Domain Model

The core domain model follows motorsport conventions with races, participants, lap timing data, and visualizations.
